RealTimeResultGroupDefinition.ColumnClassName: NtpClientConfig NtpClientConfig EmulatedDevice NtpClientResults NtpClientResults NtpClientResults NtpClientResults
RealTimeResultGroupDefinition.ColumnPropertyName: Mode SyncState DeviceCount TxPktCount RxPktCount SessionSyncdCount SessionUnsyncdCount
RealTimeResultGroupDefinition.SqlString: SELECT Port.Name AS 'Port Name', EmulatedDevice.Name AS 'Device Name', NtpClientConfig.Mode AS 'NTP Assocation Mode', NtpClientConfig.SyncState AS 'NTP Synchronized State', EmulatedDevice.DeviceCount AS 'Device Count', NtpClientResults.TxPktCount AS 'Tx Packet Count', NtpClientResults.RxPktCount AS 'Rx Packet Count', NtpClientResults.SessionSyncdCount AS 'Synchronized Session Count', NtpClientResults.SessionUnsyncdCount AS 'Unsynchronized Session Count' FROM NtpClientResults, Port, AllDevice AS EmulatedDevice, NtpClientConfig, RelationTable WHERE ( NtpClientResults.ParentHnd = NtpClientConfig.Handle AND NtpClientConfig.ParentHnd = EmulatedDevice.Handle AND RelationTable.Type = 'AffiliationPort' AND RelationTable.SourceHnd = EmulatedDevice.Handle AND RelationTable.TargetHnd = Port.Handle AND NtpClientResults.DataSetId = @DataSetId AND Port.DataSetId = @DataSetId AND EmulatedDevice.DataSetId = @DataSetId AND NtpClientConfig.DataSetId = @DataSetId AND RelationTable.DataSetId = @DataSetId ) UNION SELECT ExternalDevicePort.Name AS 'Port Name', EmulatedDevice.Name AS 'Device Name', NtpClientConfig.Mode AS 'NTP Assocation Mode', NtpClientConfig.SyncState AS 'NTP Synchronized State', EmulatedDevice.DeviceCount AS 'Device Count', NtpClientResults.TxPktCount AS 'Tx Packet Count', NtpClientResults.RxPktCount AS 'Rx Packet Count', NtpClientResults.SessionSyncdCount AS 'Synchronized Session Count', NtpClientResults.SessionUnsyncdCount AS 'Unsynchronized Session Count' FROM NtpClientResults, ExternalDevicePort, AllDevice AS EmulatedDevice, NtpClientConfig, Port, RelationTable WHERE ( NtpClientResults.ParentHnd = NtpClientConfig.Handle AND NtpClientConfig.ParentHnd = EmulatedDevice.Handle AND RelationTable.Type = 'AffiliationPort' AND RelationTable.SourceHnd = EmulatedDevice.Handle AND RelationTable.TargetHnd = Port.Handle AND NtpClientResults.DataSetId = @DataSetId AND ExternalDevicePort.DataSetId = @DataSetId AND EmulatedDevice.DataSetId = @DataSetId AND NtpClientConfig.DataSetId = @DataSetId AND Port.DataSetId = @DataSetId AND RelationTable.DataSetId = @DataSetId )
